title: Obama guidance, press schedule Oct. 13, 2015. Attorney General Loretta Lynch meeting
text:
Below, from the White House….
THE WHITE HOUSE
Office of the Press Secretary
FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE
October 12, 2015
DAILY GUIDANCE AND PRESS SCHEDULE FOR
TUESDAY, OCTOBER 13, 2015
In the morning, the President and the Vice President will receive the Presidential Daily Briefing in the Oval Office. This meeting is closed press.
In the afternoon, the President will meet with Attorney General Loretta Lynch in the Oval Office. This meeting is closed press.
In-Town Travel Pool
Wires: AP, Reuters, Bloomberg
Wire Photos: AP, Reuters, AFP
TV Corr & Crew: CBS
Print: Houston Chronicle
Radio: ABC
